Found this while trying to find the problem of L831-038. But it is an
independent problem ...

When we have the a project with a main (main.adb), which depends another
package (p.adb/s), and p.adb is changed, the second step of gnatprove
does nothing today.

Instead, gnat2why should be called on both main.adb and p.adb.

assigned to kanig, prio 4
for a reproducer

